title: Loopmasters - Deadmau5 XFER WAV Sound Pack
description:
Loopmasters - Deadmau5 XFER - this is a CD that contains over 3,000 drum samples for music producers, featuring a variety of WAV loops and single hits, ready to be loaded into any popular music software. 

This drive is designed specifically for sound producers, contains WAV loops and van shots and is compatible with any popular software serving for writing music. Formats: Wav and Rex2 Tech Specs: Over 500 Mb of Sample Content 336 Loops 425 Kick Drum Samples 229 Clap samples 1500 + percussive samples 322 Hihat samples, 158 Snare drum samples 100 + Cymbal and Cymbal-effect samples 227 synth / tonal samples 336 Bonus Rex Loops (Download Only) composed and engineered by Duda and the mau5 themselves. 

Main characteristics Deadmau5 XFER: 
- More than 500 MB of samples 
- 336 loops 
- 425 Kick Drums 
- 229 Clap sounds 
- 1500 + percussion sounds 
- 322 percussion 
- 158 snare drums 
- 100 + Cymbals and Sound Effects 
- 227 synth / tonal sounds 
- Bonus 336 Rex loops. 

Scanned with Avast and shown to be free of viruses. Enjoy!
